### 1. 详细健康检查（调用 Agent API，更新缓存）
GET http://localhost:8080/agent/health
Accept: application/json

### 2. 快速健康检查（从缓存读取，毫秒级）
GET http://localhost:8080/agent/health/quick
Accept: application/json

### 3. 获取健康检查缓存详情
GET http://localhost:8080/agent/health/cache
Accept: application/json

### 4. 强制刷新健康检查
POST http://localhost:8080/agent/health/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. 获取可用模型列表（动态）
GET http://localhost:8080/agent/available-models
Accept: application/json

### 6. 获取可用工具列表
GET http://localhost:8080/agent/tools
Accept: application/json

### 7. 调试聊天（完整入参+出参写入 scripts/agent-debug-response.json）
POST http://localhost:8080/agent/debug-chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "你好，我在五角场附近，有什么兼职吗？",
  "conversationId": "debug-001",
  "scenario": "candidate-consultation",
  "userId":"test-user-123"
}

### 8. 流式聊天测试（与 Dashboard 对话测试页面调用的接口一致）
### 接口：POST /test-suite/chat/ai-stream（Vercel AI SDK 格式）
POST http://localhost:8080/test-suite/chat/ai-stream
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "scenario": "candidate-consultation",
  "saveExecution": false,
  "chatId": "health-check-test-001",
  "userId": "dashboard-test-user",
  "messages": [
    {
      "id": "msg-1",
      "role": "user",
      "parts": [{ "type": "text", "text": "你好，我想找兼职" }]
    }
  ]
}
